title: La.Jetee.1963.(French short that inspired 12 Monkeys)[English Su
description:
La Jet&eacute;e (1962)
Directed and written by: Chris Marker

Genre: Sci-Fi / Short

Plot Summary: Earth lies ruined in the aftermath of a nuclear war. The few surviving humans begin researching time travel, in hopes of sending someone back to the pre-war world in search of food, supplies, and hopefully some sort of solution to mankind's imminent demise.

Info: 'La Jet&eacute;e' is comprised entirely of still shot photography (except one barely noticable scene where you can see the character blink and slightly move). 'La Jet&eacute;e' inspired and influenced Terry Gilliam to make the movie "12 monkeys".
